  <brief_title>Comparing Effectiveness of Merocel and Packing With Tranexamic Acid in the Management of Anterior Epistaxis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Evaluation of Effectiveness of Nasal Compression With Tranexamic Acid Compared to Simple Nasal Compression and Merocel Packing</official_title>
