  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of this study is evaluate whether superior nasal compression with tranexamic acid to
      simple nasal compression and Merocel packing.

      In this study, patients who presented with non-traumatic anterior epistaxis to emergency
      departments will be included in this study. Three different therapy option are created;
      first, nasal compression with tranexamic acid, second, simple nasal compression without any
      drugs. And third, packing with Merocel.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
